text: Ah, this unit is so good! Yuta complimenting Jisung and Jisung getting all flustered was sweet, Hendery and Jeno laughing so much at Johnny and Yuta's jokes makes me smile and Johnny being proud when Jungwoo did the same pose as him was just a perfect NCT moment. It was great hearing them talk about how surprising it was that the youngest NCT member, Jisung, has the deepest voice of them all. He's really been bias wrecking me lately because I love deep voices. 'The Bat' showed off his excellent singing and rapping so well! While I'm sad Taeil missed out because of his injury, hopefully one day he'll be able to perform this song with the rest of the unit!
